- Why fake IDs?
- Wait, fake IDs?

39:12.686 --> 39:14.562
- Look, I used them
on the road, okay?

39:14.604 --> 39:16.106
I didn't want Tucker to find me

39:16.147 --> 39:18.400
before I could get
the cash to pay him back.

39:19.567 --> 39:21.736
- Okay, well,
are you still in debt?

39:22.570 --> 39:24.656
- No. No, I...

39:25.365 --> 39:27.867
I spent the last year
earning enough to pay him.

39:29.703 --> 39:32.872
Look, I only play
for beer money, now, I swear.

39:34.165 --> 39:36.209
- Alright.

39:36.251 --> 39:38.169
- I'm sorry that you felt

39:38.211 --> 39:40.255
like you had to hide
all this from us.

39:41.172 --> 39:44.259
And I'm sorry that it had
to come out this way.

39:48.179 --> 39:49.931
Everything's out
in the open now.

39:51.933 --> 39:54.644
It's okay, it's okay, come here.

